Package rocks.xmpp.extensions.disco.model.items

Interface DiscoverableItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Addressable, Item, ResultSetItem, ServiceDiscoveryNode
    public interface DiscoverableItem
extends Item, ResultSetItem
    A Service Discovery item which has an id, in order to provide a limited result set.

    Implementations of this class are provided by the ItemProvider, which in turn is used by the AbstractServiceDiscoveryManager to returned a limited result set to the requesting entity (only if a limited result set has been requested).
